
### Tier 3 - Other coding mutations in proto-oncogenes, tumor suppressor genes or cancer census genes

- A total of __`r nrow(report_data$variants_tier3_display)`__ unique, somatic variant(s) in the tumor sample are found within known proto-oncogenes, tumor suppressor genes or cancer census genes.
<br><br>

```{r tier3, echo=F}
myOptions <- list(paging = F,pageLength=10, searching=T,caching=F)
if(nrow(report_data$variants_tier3_display) > 10){
  myOptions <- list(paging = T,pageLength=10, searching=T,caching=F)
}
if(nrow(report_data$variants_tier3_display) > 0){
  DT::datatable(report_data$variants_tier3_display, options = myOptions, escape=F, extensions = "Responsive")
}

```
